PART 12 — aligned(n) Attribute
Code
struct B {    char a;    int b;} __attribute__((aligned(16)));
Meaning
Struct starts on 16-byte boundary.Size may round to multiple of 16.

PART 13 — Packed + Aligned Together
Code
struct C {    char a;    int b;} __attribute__((packed, aligned(4)));
Meaning
Internal packing tightType alignment at least 4

